Available Tools: get_temperature | get_humidity | get_wind_speed | get_uv_index
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "location": "string", "unit": "celsius|fahrenheit" }
Response Schema: { "value": number, "unit": "string", "timestamp": "string" }
---
Question: What is the temperature in Berlin right now?
Call: { "func_call": "get_temperature", "location": "Berlin", "unit": "celsius" }
Response: { "value": 15.7, "unit": "celsius", "timestamp": "2023-10-27T12:20:00Z" }

Question: How hot is it in Los Angeles? Use Fahrenheit.
Call: { "func_call": "get_temperature", "location": "Los Angeles", "unit": "fahrenheit" }
Response: { "value": 79.4, "unit": "fahrenheit", "timestamp": "2023-10-27T08:45:00Z" }

Question: Give me the current temperature for Paris in Celsius.
Call: { "func_call": "get_temperature", "location": "Paris", "unit": "celsius" }
Response: { "value": 18.2, "unit": "celsius", "timestamp": "2023-10-27T13:10:00Z" }

